summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2013 NISSAN VERSA. WHILE ATTEMPTING TO MAKE A LEFT TURN, AN ONCOMING VEHICLE CRASHED INTO THE PASSENGER SIDE OF THE CONTACT'S VEHICLE. THE DRIVER SIDE AIR BAG DID NOT DEPLOY, BUT THE PASSENGER SIDE AIR BAG DEPLOYED. THE MANUFACTURER WAS NOT NOTIFIED. THE VEHICLE WAS TOWED. THERE WERE NO INJURIES AND A POLICE REPORT WAS NOT FILED. THE APPROXIMATE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 186,000.
